  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">WID Energy Africa - providing rural communities in Zambia with 20 community-based distribution hubs for Pay-As-You-Go smartphones which will be pre-loaded with starting bundles</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">WidEnergy Africa aims to provide rural communities in Zambia with 20 community-based distribution hubs for Pay-As-You-Go smartphones which will be pre-loaded with starting bundles. These hubs will be a one-stop shop for community energy, water and connectivity.

WidEnergy Africa also plans to implement community-based digital inclusion hubs which will provide digital skills training to help customers learn how to use the internet and access essential digital services.&#x200B; Free trainings will be organised monthly, with a particular focus on underserved groups such as women and persons with disabilities.</narrative>
  </description>
